WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.550
In order to establish connections
with investors you have to network.

00:00:03.550 --> 00:00:05.620
The question is, where do you start?

00:00:05.620 --> 00:00:08.910
And you can start by going to events and
meeting people there,

00:00:08.910 --> 00:00:12.940
you can start through your own personal
network that's already in place, but

00:00:12.940 --> 00:00:15.670
the key thing is you have
to establish that network.

00:00:15.670 --> 00:00:18.410
And there are various tools you
can use to help with that, but

00:00:18.410 --> 00:00:19.860
there's no way around it.

00:00:19.860 --> 00:00:24.210
Investors are receiving pitches and
business plans from people all the time.

00:00:24.210 --> 00:00:26.920
And what they're really going to
end up paying attention to

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:29.620
is something whether some personal
connection with the idea.

00:00:29.620 --> 00:00:32.700
There's a personal connection
with whoever the founder is and

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:33.310
that's what you need

